---
---
<section id="inscription" class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 bg-terracotta grain-overlay overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative circles -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-64 h-64 rounded-full border border-cream/20"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-48 h-48 rounded-full border border-cream/20"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <p class="text-cream/80 uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-xs font-medium mb-4">Samedi 3 octobre 2026</p>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-cream mb-6">
      Devenez Héritier de Copilos
    </h2>
    <p class="text-cream/90 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      Les places sont limitées. Inscrivez-vous dès maintenant pour relever
      le défi et rejoindre la communauté des Tectosages.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://chrono-start.com/"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-cream hover:bg-linen text-charcoal px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-sans font-bold text-base sm:text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-charcoal/20"
    >
      S'inscrire maintenant
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
